feedback:
Very comprehensive program...everything was covered thoroughly.
My only observation is about the questionnaire. Some questions related to specific issues (e.g., depression, violence/weapons) had other unrelated issues included. It was hard for to say yes or not or agree or disagree. Other than that, it was great and the various categories made it very interesting, educational along with your short videos clips.

I loved tracking my food. I felt more accountable (to myself). I enjoyed the customizable fields for nightly inventory. I'm not overweight so I don't need the additional features. That's why I never subscribed and I'm letting go.
